extendedInfo.description: This conference will address critical market research business issues faced by agencies doing business across borders and throughout the globe. Perspectives and insights will be shared from various geographic regions on: legal and regulatory requirements; respondent and client issues; privacy/confidentiality/disclosure and data security concerns; international standards; and online, mobile and other research methodologies.CASRO, Global Conference, The Mosaic of Global Research, Miami, 2012, ARIA
